## Phase 5: Fix Admin Panel — Proper Access Control

> **Goal**: Admin panel sirf `isSystem` role wale users access kar saken. Redirect sahi path pe ho.

### Changes

#### [MODIFY] [admin/layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/[businessSlug]/admin/layout.tsx)
- Fix redirect from `/dashboard` to correct path
- Pass slug to [getBusinessContext()](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/lib/getBusinessContext.ts#5-50)

```diff
 export default async function AdminLayout({
   children,
+  params,
 }: {
   children: React.ReactNode;
+  params: Promise<{ businessSlug: string }>;
 }) {
-    const ctx = await getBusinessContext();
+    const { businessSlug } = await params;
+    const ctx = await getBusinessContext(businessSlug);
 
     if (!hasPermission(ctx, 'admin', 'view')) {
-        redirect('/dashboard');
+        redirect(`/${businessSlug}`);
     }
```

#### [MODIFY] [adminActions.ts](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/adminActions.ts)
- Ensure all admin functions check [hasPermission(ctx, 'admin', 'view')](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/lib/permissions.ts#8-34) 
- Remove any `overrides` references

### ✅ Checkpoint
Non-admin user se URL me `/admin` type karo. Dashboard pe redirect hona chahiye. Admin se admin panel accessible ho.

