## Phase 6: Add Permission Guards to Critical Server Actions

> **Goal**: Server actions me bhi permission check ho, sirf client-side filtering kaafi nahi.

### Current State
Most server actions call [getBusinessContext()](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/lib/getBusinessContext.ts#5-50) (which verifies auth + business membership) but DON'T check specific module permissions. For example `getOrders()` doesn't check [hasPermission(ctx, 'orders', 'view')](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/lib/permissions.ts#8-34).

### Changes

#### Strategy (1-2 files at a time)
Add [hasPermission](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/lib/permissions.ts#8-34) check to the top of each action function. Pattern:

```typescript
const ctx = await getBusinessContext();
if (!hasPermission(ctx, 'orders', 'view')) {
    throw new Error('UNAUTHORIZED');
}
```

**Priority actions to guard:**
1. [app/actions/adminActions.ts](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/adminActions.ts) — [getRoles](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/adminActions.ts#13-36), [createRole](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/adminActions.ts#37-73), [deleteRole](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/adminActions.ts#74-105), [getTeamMembers](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/adminActions.ts#110-131), [addTeamMember](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/adminActions.ts#132-246)
2. [app/actions/dashboard.ts](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/dashboard.ts) — `getDashboardData`
3. [app/actions/sales/orders.ts](file:///c:/Users/User/Desktop/safcha%20dash%202/safcha-dashboard/app/actions/sales/orders.ts) — all CRUD
4. `app/actions/finance/` — all CRUD
5. Other actions — follow same pattern

> [!NOTE]  
> This is a larger phase. Each action file can be done independently. We add permission checks action-by-action. No need to do all at once.

### ✅ Checkpoint
Non-admin user se directly server action call karo (via browser console or URL). `UNAUTHORIZED` error aana chahiye.

