## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
No existing test suite found in the project. Manual testing is the primary verification method.

### Manual Verification  
Each phase has a **✅ Checkpoint** section. After completing each phase:
1. Run `npm run dev` 
2. Follow the checkpoint steps
3. Confirm working before moving to next phase
4. Tell me "Phase X done, checkpoint passed" to proceed

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Har phase ke baad app test karo. Next phase tab start hogi jab aap confirm karo ke current phase ka checkpoint pass hua. Ye isliye ke agar koi issue aaye to use turant fix kar saken, baad me debug karna mushkil hota.
